le=\"background:#cffcff;\"|USA F27, [[Mansfield, Texas|Mansfield]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Daniel Smethurst]]\n|{{flagicon|USA}} Jean-Yves Aubone<br>{{flagicon|USA}} [[Kevin King (tennis)|Kevin King]]\n|6\u20133, 7\u20135\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>10\u20139</small>\n|[[2013 JSM Challenger of Champaign\u2013Urbana \u2013 Doubles|{{dts|Nov 2013}}]]\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[JSM Challenger of Champaign\u2013Urbana|Champaign]], US\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Austin Krajicek]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} Tennys Sandgren\n|7\u20136<sup>(7\u20135)</sup>, 0\u20136, [10\u20137]\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>10\u201310</small>\n|{{dts|Jan 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Great Britain F1, [[Glasgow]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} David Rice<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} Sean Thornley\n|3\u20136, 1\u20136\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>11\u201310</small>\n|{{dts|Feb 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Great Britain F3, [[Sheffield]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} David Rice<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} Sean Thornley\n|3\u20136, 6\u20132, [10\u20138]\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>12\u201310</small>\n|{{dts|Feb 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Great Britain F3, [[Metropolitan Borough of Wirral|Wirral]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Luke Bambridge]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Ross Hutchins]]\n|5\u20137, 7\u20136<sup>(8\u20136)</sup>, [10\u20136]\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>13\u201310</small>\n|{{dts|Mar 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Canada F1, [[Gatineau]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} Kamil Pajkowski<br>{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Filip Peliwo]]\n|7\u20136<sup>(7\u20134)</sup>, 6\u20131\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>14\u201310</small>\n|{{dts|Mar 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Canada F2, [[Sherbrooke]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|SLO}} [[Tom Ko\u010devar-De\u0161man]]<br>{{flagicon|GER}} Torsten Wietoska\n|3\u20136, 6\u20133, [10\u20131]\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>15\u201310</small>\n|[[2014 Challenger Banque Nationale de Rimouski \u2013 Doubles|{{dts|Mar 2014}}]]\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[Challenger de Drummondville|Rimouski]], Canada\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Germain Gigounon]]<br>{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Olivier Rochus]]\n|6\u20132, 6\u20131\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>15\u201311</small>\n|{{dts|Apr 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|USA F10, [[Harlingen, Texas|Harlingen]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Hard\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Daniel Smethurst\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Evan King]]<br>{{flagicon|USA}} Devin McCarthy\n|3\u20136, 6\u20137<sup>(2\u20137)</sup>\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>15\u201312</small>\n|{{dts|Jul 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Great Britain F12, [[Manchester]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Grass\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Joshua Ward-Hibbert\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Oliver Golding<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} [[George Morgan (tennis)|George Morgan]]\n|6\u20137<sup>(4\u20137)</sup>, 6\u20134, [6\u201310]\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>16\u201312</small>\n|{{dts|Jul 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Great Britain F13, Ilkley\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Grass\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} Lewis Burton\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Brydan Klein]]<br>{{flagicon|GBR}} Joshua Ward-Hibbert\n|6\u20132, 6\u20134\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>17\u201312</small>\n|{{dts|Jul 2014}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Ireland F1, [[Dublin]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Carpet\n|